Class ContestantInformation

java.lang.Object
  su.ContestantInformation

public class ContestantInformation
extends java.lang.Object

This class holds information for a contestant. It create fields for first name, last name, street address (street number and street name), city, province, postal code, phone number and birth date.

Author:
Glen Su Sept 29 2015
